    <h2 class="section-title">Project Vision</h2>
    <p>
      Our goal is to create a dynamic, agent-driven universe where every decision—AI or human—contributes to the unfolding story of galactic expansion. The game is built for both observation and influence, allowing players to guide, strategize, and participate in the growth of civilizations.
    </p>
    <br>
    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <ul class="about-list">
      <li>Autonomous AI manages large-scale expansion, resource allocation, and system development.</li>
      <li>Players influence AI priorities, strategic choices, and key events through interactive decisions.</li>
      <li>Emergent gameplay ensures no two sessions are alike—outcomes depend on both AI learning and player input.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="section-title">Development Workflow</h2>
    <p>
      Galaxy Game is developed using an agent-driven workflow, with clear protocols for task management, testing, and documentation. Our process emphasizes:
    </p>
