      <li>Transparent status tracking and planning (<code>docs/agent/CURRENT_STATUS.md</code>)</li>
      <li>Modular, maintainable code and SCSS for a consistent UI</li>
      <li>Automated and manual testing to ensure quality</li>
      <li>Continuous improvement based on player and developer feedback</li>
    </ul>

